Package ipp.estg.dto

Class UserResponseDto

java.lang.Object
ipp.estg.dto.UserResponseDto
public class UserResponseDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user response. This class is used to encapsulate user information in a format suitable for sending as a response.
